{"tid":2044340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紐約抗議明州非裔命案衝突嚴重 紐約州長要州檢察長徹查","createTime":"2020-05-31T05:09:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T07:54:05.000Z","uid":78519,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3e173ba512c22e8fe1b537a9034c9ee3290e34cc","tid":2044340,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:09:16.000Z","msg":"紐約市超過3000民眾昨日下午至晚間再在下東城及布碌崙(布魯克林)進行集會，抗議明州非洲裔男子佛洛伊德(George Floyd)遭白人警察沙文(Derek Chauvin)膝蓋壓頸致死，但至晚間警方與民眾產生大規模衝突，超過200名抗議者被捕，並有多名警員受傷；州長葛謨(Andrew Cuomo)30日宣布將由州檢察長詹樂霞(Letitia James)徹查當天抗議細節。<br />\n<br />\n葛謨表示，州檢察長是民選的獨立機構職位，可以在調查過程中保持公正立場。<br />\n<br />\n葛謨指出，種族歧視在美國歷史上存在數百年，他與抗議者站在一起，對警方執法不公表達憤慨，但他也強調，暴力絕不是解決問題的答案，暴力甚至會遮掩大家想表達的追求公正這一信號和使命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/6968382/article-%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e6%8a%97%e8%ad%b0%e6%98%8e%e5%b7%9e%e9%9d%9e%e8%a3%94%e5%91%bd%e6%a1%88%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81%e5%9a%b4%e9%87%8d-%e8%91%9b%e8%ac%a8%e8%a6%81%e5%b7%9e%e6%aa%a2%e5%af%9f%e9%95%b7%e5%be%b9/?ref=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%B8%BD%E8%A6%BD&amp;ismobile=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2F6968382%2Farticle-%25e7%25b4%2590%25e7%25b4%2584%25e6%258a%2597%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%2598%258e%25e5%25b7%259e%25e9%259d%259e%25e8%25a3%2594%25e5%2591%25bd%25e6%25a1%2588%25e8%25a1%259d%25e7%25aa%2581%25e5%259a%25b4%25e9%2587%258d-%25e8%2591%259b%25e8%25ac%25a8%25e8%25a6%2581%25e5%25b7%259e%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e5%25af%259f%25e9%2595%25b7%25e5%25be%25b9%2F%3Fref%3D%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E8%25A6%25BD%26ismobile%3Dtrue&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdDH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=e2e2edcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/6968382/article-%e7%b4%90%e7%b4%84%e6%8a%97%e8%ad%b0%e6%98%8e%e5%b7%9e%e9%9d%9e%e8%a3%94%e5%91%bd%e6%a1%88%e8%a1%9d%e7%aa%81%e5%9a%b4%e9%87%8d-%e8%91%9b%e8%ac%a8%e8%a6%81%e5%b7%9e%e6%aa%a2%e5%af%9f%e9%95%b7%e5%be%b9/?ref=%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B_%E6%96%B0